      <h2>Community Services</h2>
      <p class="section-intro">
        We offer a variety of community services to support seniors, families, and students in Mississauga. Our programs are designed to help you connect with the community, access essential resources, and enhance your quality of life.
      </p>

      <!-- ËÄÅÂπ¥‰∫∫ÊúçÂä°ÈÉ®ÂàÜ -->
      <h3>Senior Services</h3>
      
      <div class="services-list">
        <!-- ËÄÅ‰∫∫ÂÖ¨ÂØìÁî≥ËØ∑ -->
        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-header">
            <h4>Senior Housing Application</h4>
          </div>
          <div class="service-content">
            <p>Assistance with applications for senior housing options, including subsidized housing and retirement residences.</p>
            <p>Our staff can help you understand eligibility requirements, complete application forms, and prepare necessary documentation.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- ËÄÅ‰∫∫ÂêÉËçØË°•Âä©Áî≥ËØ∑ -->
