          <div class="service-content">
            <p>Help with applications for drug coverage programs specifically designed for seniors.</p>
            <p>We can assist you in determining which drug benefit programs you qualify for and guide you through the application process.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- ËÄÅ‰∫∫ÈáëÂèäËÄÅ‰∫∫Ë°•Âä©ÈáëÁî≥ËØ∑ -->
        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-header">
            <h4>Old Age Security & GIS </h4>
          </div>
          <div class="service-content">
            <p>Assistance with applications for Old Age Security (OAS) and Guaranteed Income Supplement (GIS) benefits.</p>
            
            <div class="document-list-section">
              <h5>Required Documents</h5>
              <ul class="document-list">
                <li>PR Card & Landing Paper, or Citizenship Card/Certificate</li>
                <li>Social Insurance Number (SIN), all current & previous passports</li>
                <li>Spouse name, date of birth, and Social Insurance Number (SIN)</li>
                <li>Current address and contact number</li>
                <li>Marriage Certificate (if married)</li>
                <li>List of residency, within and outside of Canada, since age of 18</li>
                <li>Bank account information for Direct Deposit</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- ÈÄÄ‰ºëÈáëÁî≥ËØ∑ -->
